Is slaving over a hot forge not your cup of tea? For the less physically-minded humans comes the still-challenging human tailoring. Six lovely, and unique, cultural robes that can be worn by INT casters of all races.<p>
While intermediate combines can be performed by a variety of folks, the final robe combines must be performed by a real, live human. (Illusioning into human form won't do the trick, nor will reanimating a corpse and having it perform the combine for you.) Trithalis Leredar (-265, -505, W. Freeport), will only give out no drop robe patterns to true humans who target Trithalis and say "I want a robe pattern" <p><br><div align="right">Last Modified By: Niami Denmother&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

		Last Modified on: 2003-05-19 06:56:49&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></div><br>
